      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/zambia-aims-to-resolve-debt-revamp-standoff-within-three-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚财政部一位高级官员表示，赞比亚计划在未来三个月内解决债权人之间的僵局，该僵局导致债务重组工作陷入停滞。]]></description>
